			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Go to Moonrise Docks -90; 5; -187\r\nTalk to the Dock Guard Jumper\r\nUse Tadpole power to have him jump into the water\r\nTalk to the Dock Guard Observer and tell him the other guard jumped\r\nFollow the Observer into and out of the tower (it's controlled by anubis, so his movement does not update if he is not loaded)\r\nObserve him looking over the dock edge."
				},
